headline: PSE&G Ranked #1 for Residential Electric in the East among Large Utilities in J.D. Power 2025 Customer Satisfaction Study for 4th Consecutive Year
summary: Public Service Electric & Gas, New Jersey's largest utility, has once again been recognized as the highest-ranked utility in customer satisfaction among large electric utilities in the East Region, according to the J.D. Power 2025 Electric Utility Residential Customer Satisfaction Study℠. This marks the fourth consecutive year PSE&G has earned the top position.
